doctype html
html
	head
		meta(charset="utf-8")
		meta(name="viewport", content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1")
		title #{app.appname} | Login
		include ../../layout/cgHeader.pug

		style.
			.login-container {
				max-width: 420px;
				width: 100%;
			}

			.content-wrapper {
				background: url('/resources/assets/img/logo/bgnd/cloud.jpg') no-repeat center center fixed !important;
				background-size: cover !important;
			}

	body( class="hold-transition layout-top-nav" )
		.wrapper

			// Content Wrapper
			div.content-wrapper
				div.content
					div.container-fluid

						// Add vertical spacing
						//- div.row.justify-content-center.mt-5
						//- div.row.justify-content-center.align-items-center(style="min-height: calc(100vh - 120px);")
						//- div.row.justify-content-center.align-items-center.px-3(style="min-height: calc(100vh - 120px);")
						div.row.justify-content-center.align-items-start.px-3.pt-4(style="min-height: calc(100vh - 120px);")
							div.col-md-12.col-sm-6.col-12

								br
								br

								div.card.card-primary
									div.card-header.text-center
										h3.card-title Help

									div.card-body
										p.login-box-msg.text-center.mb-4
											| Contact System Admin
										div.px-4.pt-3
											p
												| The 
												b Client Login Module
												|  is designed to provide secure access exclusively for registered clients. 
												| Through this portal, clients can access their personalized dashboard, review account details, and interact 
												| with available services.

											p
												| Login credentials (username and password) are unique to each client and verified through a secure 
												| authentication process. The system validates the provided credentials against stored records, ensuring 
												| only authorized users are granted access.

											p
												| Once logged in, clients gain access to modules such as 
												b billing
												| , 
												b requests
												| , 
												b notifications
												| , and 
												b account management
												| . Session handling ensures that all activities are tracked for security and 
												| audit purposes.

											p
												| To enhance security, failed login attempts are logged and can trigger alerts or temporary account lockouts. 
												| Clients are encouraged to maintain strong passwords and update them regularly through the account settings.

											p
												| The login page is intended solely for 
												b client access
												| . Administrative and staff modules are accessible 
												| through a separate portal to maintain system integrity and role-based permissions.

											p
												| Use the 
												b Login
												|  form to enter your credentials. Upon successful authentication, you will be redirected 
												| to your dashboard where you can explore the services available to you.

									div.card-footer.text-center
										div.row
											div.col-4
												a(href="/") Home
											div.col-4
												//- a(href="/auth/forgot") Forgot password?
											div.col-4
												//- a(href="/auth/help") Help

			include ../../layout/cgFooter-no-session.pug
			include ../../layout/cgJs.pug

	script.
		$(document).ready(function(){
			console.log("Page ready");
		});